# ✈️ Agentic AI-Based Travel Planning Assistant

An intelligent travel planning system built using **LangChain**, **LangGraph**, and **Groq LLaMA 3.3** that autonomously plans complete trip itineraries based on user preferences.

---

## 🧠 What is Agentic AI?

Unlike a standard chatbot that answers one question at a time, an **Agentic AI** system reasons across multiple steps and autonomously decides which tools to call to complete a complex task.

In this project, the agent receives a travel query like:

> _"Plan a 3-day trip to Delhi from Hyderabad within ₹20,000"_

And autonomously:

1. Searches for flights
2. Recommends hotels
3. Discovers tourist attractions
4. Fetches live weather data
5. Calculates total budget
6. Generates a complete day-wise itinerary

---

## 🏗️ Project Structure

```
travel_agent/
├── data/
│   ├── flights.json        # Flight dataset (30 records)
│   ├── hotels.json         # Hotel dataset (40 records)
│   └── places.json         # Tourist places dataset (40 records)
├── travel_agent.ipynb      # Development notebook
├── app.py                  # Streamlit web application
├── requirements.txt        # Python dependencies
├── .env                    # API keys (not pushed to GitHub)
├── .gitignore
└── README.md
```

---

## ⚙️ Tech Stack

| Component        | Technology                       |
| ---------------- | -------------------------------- |
| LLM              | Groq LLaMA 3.3 70B (free)        |
| Agent Framework  | LangGraph (ReAct Agent)          |
| Tool Integration | LangChain Tools                  |
| Weather API      | Open-Meteo (free, no key needed) |
| UI               | Streamlit                        |
| Language         | Python 3.x                       |

---

## 🛠️ Tools Built

| Tool               | Description                                                          |
| ------------------ | -------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| `search_flights`   | Filters flights.json by source/destination, returns cheapest options |
| `recommend_hotels` | Filters hotels.json by city and price, returns top-rated hotels      |
| `find_places`      | Filters places.json by city, returns top attractions by rating       |
| `get_weather`      | Calls Open-Meteo API for 5-day live weather forecast                 |
| `estimate_budget`  | Calculates total trip cost (flight + hotel + food & transport)       |

---

## 🚀 Live Demo
👉 [Click here to try the app](https://travel-planning-agent-ldz5zj94siwt9krvu24quq.streamlit.app)

## 🚀 Setup & Installation

### 1. Clone the repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/hamzashaikh-ai/travel-planning-agent
cd travel-planning-agent
```

### 2. Install dependencies

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

### 3. Set up API key

Create a `.env` file in the project root:

```
GROQ_API_KEY=your_groq_api_key_here
```

Get your free Groq API key at: https://console.groq.com

### 4. Run the Streamlit app

```bash
streamlit run app.py
```

